  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    OPSS coronavirus (COVID-19) guidance for business and local authorities
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance on how OPSS is supporting businesses and local authorities and protecting consumers during the COVID-19 pandemic.</p>

  </div>
</div>

